        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10901.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "今、春の花まつりをやってるんだって。\nいろんな色の花が咲いてて、花冠も作れるみたい。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10901.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "……美空が好きそう。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10901.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "美空",
      "text": "うん。\n好き。",
      "storySprites": [
        {
          "id": "ah",
          "src": "images/assets/char/h10202.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "ai",
          "src": "images/assets/char/i10901.webp",
          "opacity": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "speaker": "夜空",
      "text": "じゃあ、美空が行けばいい。",
